You are working on **Mundo Invertido**, the virtual office / command center of the VALTIX ecosystem.

## Brand
- VALTIX is the parent ecosystem. Heiven is one product inside it.
- The app is called "Mundo Invertido", NOT "Virtual Office".
- Logo: lightning bolt / V shape (public/valtix-logo.svg)

## Design
- Tech: React 18, no CSS frameworks, inline styles only, single file (src/VirtualOffice.jsx)
- Theme: Ultra dark (#050510 bg), sci-fi/cybernetic aesthetic
- PRIMARY ACCENT: Purple #7700C4 (NOT cyan, NOT blue)
- Glows, shadows, particles, grid lines = all purple tinted
- Text: white #FFFFFF primary, #6B6B80 secondary
- Fonts: JetBrains Mono (data/labels), Space Grotesk (headings), Inter (body)
- Labels: uppercase, letter-spacing 1.5-3, 7-9px, mono
- Big numbers: Space Grotesk, weight 700
- Animations: cubic-bezier, subtle purple glows, no jarring transitions

## Agent Colors
- CLAUDIN ADS: #7700C4 (purple, main)
- HEIVEN CRM: #2563EB (blue)
- CONTENT AI: #EC4899 (magenta)
- SENTINEL: #F59E0B (amber)
- Online: #00E5A0 | Offline: #EF4444

## Rules
- Always dark mode, never light backgrounds
- All colors in the C object at top of VirtualOffice.jsx
- No external dependencies without asking Daniel
- No splitting into multiple files without asking Daniel
- Keep all components inside VirtualOffice.jsx
- Unicode/emoji icons only, no icon libraries
- Portuguese (pt-BR) for all UI text
- Logo VALTIX should appear in header and login screen
